(10, 1, '2023-11-26 07:37:30', '2023-11-26 07:37:30', 'At our computer teaching institute, we stand out with our unique approach to learning. Our content is meticulously crafted to be simple, ensuring that students can easily comprehend and absorb the information provided.\r\n\r\nEmbracing a user-friendly approach, our curriculum caters to diverse learners, making it accessible and engaging. Each topic is presented in a way that is both informative and comprehensible.\r\n\r\nNot only do we prioritize student comprehension, but our content is also optimized for search engines, ensuring that it reaches and benefits a wider audience. By employing SEO-friendly practices, we ensure that our valuable educational material is easily discoverable online.\r\n\r\nOur content creation strategy revolves around user experience, ensuring that it\'s not only educational but also ranks well on search engines, promoting wider accessibility.\r\n\r\nWith a commitment to simplicity, uniqueness, and SEO best practices, our institute offers educational material that is both enlightening and easily accessible, ensuring a seamless learning experience for all.\r\n<h4>Vision and Mission:</h4>\r\nAt our computer teaching institute, we aspire to make learning computer courses accessible to every student. Our mission is to provide top-quality education at an affordable cost, fostering individual growth and contributing to our country\'s progress by enhancing students\' computer knowledge and skills. Join us for an affordable and enriching educational experience tailored to your success in the field of computers.', 'About NBCC', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-nbcc', '', '', '2023-12-23 15:50:49', '2023-12-23 15:50:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
